OL,6,FA couple who were part of a mob
OL,7,Foutside an asylum hotel during the
OL,8,Fsummer's riots have been freed after
OL,9,Fserving a month in prison.
OL,11,FMichelle Jibson, 45, and her partner
OL,12,FTracy Pearson, 53, were in custody
OL,13,Fafter admitting violent disorder at
OL,14,FManchester Magistrates' Court on 12
OL,15,FAugust.
OL,17,FThe pair were part of a mob outside
OL,18,Fthe Holiday Inn in Newton Heath in
OL,19,FManchester on 31 July, which was
OL,20,Fhousing asylum seekers.
