OL,6,FBottles, bricks and eggs were thrown
OL,7,Fat the hotel by the crowd outside as
OL,8,Friot police struggled to keep order
OL,9,Ffollowing the nationwide outbreak of
OL,10,Fviolence after three children were
OL,11,Fstabbed to death in Southport.
OL,13,FJibson had been shoved by a police
OL,14,Fofficer trying to disperse the crowd
OL,15,Fand reacted by shoving him back.
