OL,6,FThe court heard how Pearson had
OL,7,F"expressed some trenchant, distasteful
OL,8,Fviews, very loudly", with crowds heard
OL,9,Fto shout towards the hotel, "Dirty
OL,10,Fbastards!" and "No one wants you
OL,11,Fhere!", along with chants of "Who the
OL,12,Ff*** is Allah?" and "We want our
OL,13,Fcountry back".
OL,15,FJudge Patrick Field KC said he
OL,16,Faccepted Pearson had not acted
OL,17,Fviolently herself, but added: "This
OL,18,Flevel of intolerance was deeply
OL,19,Fshaming to everybody involved.
