OL,6,F"You were emboldened to do what you
OL,7,Fdid. This case illustrates however,
OL,8,Fhow important it is to think carefully
OL,9,Fbefore accepting all you have read
OL,10,Fonline.
OL,12,F"The online world, as you now know is
OL,13,Ffull of traps for the unwary."
