OL,6,FBut he said he accepted both women had
OL,7,Fnot acted maliciously and in the last
OL,8,Fmonth, custody had meant they had been
OL,9,Fapart for the first time in their 25-
OL,10,Fyear relationship.
OL,12,FJudge Field added: "I am of the view
OL,13,Fyou both have learned a particularly
OL,14,Fhard lesson."
